%% Golden template: synchronous request-response.
%% Source scenario: a client makes one blocking call through an API and gets a value back.
%% Solid filled arrow (->>) is a synchronous call. Dashed open arrow (-->>) is the return.
%% The +/- suffix opens and closes the activation bar in one line, which keeps activate
%% and deactivate balanced. autonumber is on because call ordering is part of the contract.
sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant Client
  participant API as API Gateway
  participant Service as Order Service
  Client->>+API: GET /orders/42
  API->>+Service: fetchOrder(42)
  Service-->>-API: order
  API-->>-Client: 200 order
